OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry start for many,
OL,6,Fbut cloudy with rain in northern
OL,7,FScotland. Warm and bright in the south
OL,8,Fat first, but clouding over in the
OL,9,Fafternoon as heavy showers move into
OL,10,Fthe east, with a risk of thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers gradually clearing
OL,13,Fthis evening, leaving cloudy skies for
OL,14,Fmany. Cloud will be low and thick in
OL,15,Fthe east, bringing drizzle, mist and
OL,16,Ffog in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
